ty matrices.\n- Develop optimization algorithms to reduce computational complexity.\n- Conduct extensive comparative analysis to validate the Vendi Score.\n\n### Step 6: Draft the Research Proposal\n**Draft Proposal:**\n- Include refined research questions, methodology, evaluation criteria, timeline, and potential challenges.\n- Ensure the proposal is clear, concise, and compelling.\n\n### Step 7: Seek Feedback\n**Feedback:**\n- Share the draft proposal with peers or mentors.\n- Incorporate feedback to improve the proposal.\n\n### Step 8: Finalize the Proposal\n**Final Proposal:**\n- Make any necessary revisions based on feedback.\n- Finalize the proposal for submission or presentation.\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  "name": "new_communication_session",\n  "arguments": {\n    "target_agent_id": "agent3",\n    "message": "I have refined the research proposal for extending and validating the Vendi Score as a general, reference-free metric for measuring diversity in machine learning. The proposal includes detailed research questions, methodology, evaluation criteria, timeline, and potential challenges. Would you like to review and provide feedback on the draft proposal?"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThis JSON object is ready to be used to communicate with agent3 for feedback on the draft proposal.\n'}, {'agent3': 'Result from the model:\nResult from the function:{"success": true, "message": "Successfully completed session f3ef0634-7509-4a9d-a5a7-f4a21b41d932", "full_chat_history": "In Session f3ef0634-7509-4a9d-a5a7-f4a21b41d932 \\nFrom agent3 to agent1: Hi agent1, I am working on refining the research proposal focusing on extending the Vendi Score to different ML domains and developing methods for automated similarity function selection. Could you provide insights or collaborate on the graph theory aspects of this research?\\n", "session_id": "### Summary of Chat History\\n\\n**Context and Participants:**\\n- **Agent3** initiated the conversation by reaching out to **Agent1** f